rComments: Best professor at U of I. Kept everyone interested.

Insanely interesting discussions on readings.  Clearly knowledgeable on the topic; her mix of eloquence w/blunt profanity (appropriate to the time period, as we learned) made lectures all the more attention-grabbing.  
 
 Assigned project using 18th c. collections online and took us to the Rare Book & Manuscript Lib - surprisingly enriching AND fun
